                     <interp inst="t18310630-267-person1923" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am father of this lad - he returned without his coat and cap, and told me what had happened; I know the prisoner, by seeing him about the neighbourhood for a long time, and I had him taken.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I am quite innocent; if the father and son knew they had seen me within three months, how was it likely I could have been to the East Indies?</p>
